{"title":"hexo博客搭建记录","date":"2020-03-08T08:51:16.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"2020年3月8日","L":"2020/03/08","MM-DD":"03-08"},"thumbnail":"/img/img2/9.jpg","link":"posts/1","comments":true,"tags":["hexo","搭建"],"categories":["技术"],"updated":"2020-03-16T13:39:49.071Z","content":"<span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-weight: 500\">\n\n<h4 id=\"👉🏻本人完整的搭建过程点击前往\"><a href=\"https://blog.csdn.net/weixin_44129672/article/details/104763893\" target=\"_blank\">👉🏻本人完整的搭建过程,点击前往</a><a href=\"#👉🏻本人完整的搭建过程点击前往\" title=\"👉🏻本人完整的搭建过程,点击前往\"></a></h4><h2 id=\"hexo\">Hexo<a href=\"#hexo\" title=\"Hexo\"></a></h2><ul><li>官网 <a href=\"https://hexo.io/zh-cn/\" target=\"_blank\">https://hexo.io/zh-cn/</a></li><li>模板 <a href=\"https://hexo.io/themes/\" target=\"_blank\">https://hexo.io/themes/</a></li></ul><h2 id=\"inside\">inside<a href=\"#inside\" title=\"inside\"></a></h2><ul><li>项目地址：<a href=\"https://github.com/ikeq/hexo-theme-inside/blob/master/README_zh-Hans.md\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/ikeq/hexo-theme-inside/blob/master/README_zh-Hans.md</a></li><li>文档地址：<a href=\"https://blog.oniuo.com/theme-inside\" target=\"_blank\">https://blog.oniuo.com/theme-inside</a></li></ul><h2 id=\"看板娘\">看板娘<a href=\"#看板娘\" title=\"看板娘\"></a></h2><ul><li>项目地址<br><a href=\"https://github.com/EYHN/hexo-helper-live2d/blob/master/README.zh-CN.md\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/EYHN/hexo-helper-live2d/blob/master/README.zh-CN.md</a></li><li>预览<br><a href=\"https://huaji8.top/post/live2d-plugin-2.0/\" target=\"_blank\">https://huaji8.top/post/live2d-plugin-2.0/</a></li><li>参数<br><a href=\"https://l2dwidget.js.org/docs/class/src/index.js~L2Dwidget.html#instance-method-init\" target=\"_blank\">https://l2dwidget.js.org/docs/class/src/index.js~L2Dwidget.html#instance-method-init</a></li></ul><br/>\n<br/>\n<br/>\n\n<h4 id=\"相关拓展和插件\">相关拓展和插件<a href=\"#相关拓展和插件\" title=\"相关拓展和插件\"></a></h4><ul><li><a href=\"https://www.jianshu.com/p/8e1cf1ca131b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.jianshu.com/p/8e1cf1ca131b</a></li><li><a href=\"https://xiaoxiami.gitbook.io/lodash/\" target=\"_blank\">lodash中文解析</a></li></ul><h4 id=\"评论系统\">评论系统<a href=\"#评论系统\" title=\"评论系统\"></a></h4><ul><li>disqus评论系统<ul><li>官网 <a href=\"https://disqus.com/\" target=\"_blank\">https://disqus.com/</a></li></ul></li><li>Valine(无广告)<ul><li>官网 <a href=\"https://valine.js.org/quickstart.html\" target=\"_blank\">https://valine.js.org/quickstart.html</a></li><li>配合<a href=\"https://leancloud.cn/\" target=\"_blank\">leancloud</a>使用</li></ul></li></ul><h4 id=\"谷歌字体\">谷歌字体<a href=\"#谷歌字体\" title=\"谷歌字体\"></a></h4><ul><li>官网预览： <a href=\"https://fonts.google.com/\" target=\"_blank\">https://fonts.google.com/</a></li><li>支持中文简体的字体：<ul><li>Noto Serif SC</li><li>Ma Shan Zheng</li><li>Zhi Mang Xing</li><li>Long Cang</li><li>Liu Jian Mao Cao</li><li>ZCOOL KuaiLe</li><li>Noto Sans SC</li><li>ZCOOL XiaoWei</li></ul></li></ul><h4 id=\"音乐插件\">音乐插件<a href=\"#音乐插件\" title=\"音乐插件\"></a></h4><ul><li>插入音乐和视频<br><code>npm install hexo-tag-dplayer --save</code><br><code>npm install hexo-tag-aplayer --save</code></li><li>网易云</li></ul><figure class=\"highlight html\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">iframe</span> <span class=\"attr\">frameborder</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"no\"</span> <span class=\"attr\">border</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"0\"</span> <span class=\"attr\">marginwidth</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"0\"</span> <span class=\"attr\">marginheight</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"0\"</span> <span class=\"attr\">width</span>=<span class=\"string\">330</span> <span class=\"attr\">height</span>=<span class=\"string\">86</span> <span class=\"attr\">src</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"//music.163.com/outchain/player?type=2&amp;id=442016694&amp;auto=1&amp;height=66\"</span>&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">iframe</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<ul><li>网易云歌单</li></ul><figure class=\"highlight html\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">iframe</span> <span class=\"attr\">frameborder</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"no\"</span> <span class=\"attr\">border</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"0\"</span> <span class=\"attr\">marginwidth</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"0\"</span> <span class=\"attr\">marginheight</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"0\"</span> <span class=\"attr\">width</span>=<span class=\"string\">330</span> <span class=\"attr\">height</span>=<span class=\"string\">450</span> <span class=\"attr\">src</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"//music.163.com/outchain/player?type=0&amp;id=997386069&amp;auto=1&amp;height=430\"</span>&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">iframe</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n</span>\n","prev":{"title":"这一生，还剩多少来日方长","link":"posts/5"},"plink":"https://mew.wiki.com/posts/1/","toc":[{"id":"hexo","title":"Hexo","index":"1"},{"id":"inside","title":"inside","index":"2"},{"id":"看板娘","title":"看板娘","index":"3"}]}